textObjects.text: Jack Kirby and Steve Ditko collaborated on this cover to create what is quite possibly the most iconic image in Marvel Comics' history.  Before all the clones, symbiotes and civil wars we see Spider-Man in a simpler time doing what he does best, catching crooks and saving the day.

What's left to be said about Steve Ditko and Spider-Man? Spidey's Spidey, due in large part to Ditko's early contributions, including this cover to the first all-Spider-Man comic.
